hopobject.body: What sort of work do you do? eyeforpharma latam 2018 Tallulah Belle, far r., daughter of Demi Moore, c., and Bruce Willis, not pictured, has appeared in films with both of her parents - 1995's 'The Scarlet Letter' and 2004's 'The Whole Ten Yards,' respectively - but it appears the 15-year-old may have a different career path in mind. While her older sister Rumer has been pursuing a film career, Tallulah has been busy securing a gig at Harper's Bazaar magazine.
